                     <text>
                        <paragraph>Uses</paragraph>
                        <paragraph>-helps prevent sunburn</paragraph>
                        <paragraph>-for skin that burns easily</paragraph>
                        <paragraph>-provides moderate protection against sunburn</paragraph>
                        <paragraph>-higher SPF gives more sunburn protection</paragraph>
                        <br/>
                        <paragraph>Directions</paragraph>
                        <paragraph>-for external use only</paragraph>
                        <paragraph>-when using this product keep out of eyes</paragraph>
